00:33:11,010 --> 00:33:13,220
New Zealand is the country next to Australia.

464
00:33:13,240 --> 00:33:14,370
Why are you asking grandpa such a question?

465
00:33:14,390 --> 00:33:17,000
That ignoramus, really. How dare she
disgrace people like that?

466
00:33:17,080 --> 00:33:19,990
This is the new office building
since our merger this time.

467
00:33:20,010 --> 00:33:22,690
Why come to the company? If there's time, 
shouldn't you be finding the USB quickly?

468
00:33:22,720 --> 00:33:24,000
Why are you learning Spanish?

469
00:33:24,020 --> 00:33:25,430
I want to get your mother pissed off.

470
00:33:25,450 --> 00:33:26,960
(In Spanish) Your school is shit.

471
00:33:26,970 --> 00:33:28,410
You are talking to me in Spanish now?

472
00:33:28,440 --> 00:33:30,680
I have a friend whom I have troubled a lot.

473
00:33:30,710 --> 00:33:32,450
I want to repay a little.

474
00:33:32,510 --> 00:33:34,730
No matter what, it seems like 
we'll need to get more meat.

475
00:33:34,970 --> 00:33:37,090
An eye for an eye, a tooth for a tooth.

476
00:33:37,090 --> 00:33:38,640
(In Spanish) Behave yourself, please.

477
00:33:38,640 --> 00:33:40,020
You want to challenge me, is that it?

478
00:33:40,150 --> 00:33:40,830
Credit card!

479
00:33:40,860 --> 00:33:42,310
Don't you have lots of money?

480
00:33:42,310 --> 00:33:44,230
I'll return it in a flash.
Just lend me 50 million dollar.

481
00:33:44,230 --> 00:33:45,340
Thanks.

